{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6521163f3c","title":"铲草要除根","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"48eff0cc38","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"6521163f3c"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"d6e2c0434f","name":"岑超南"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e55f824662","type":"title","text":"铲草要除根","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"adf31429c6","type":"authors","text":"北京大学岑超南","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"375d333509","type":"subtitle","text":"（岑超南：北京大学物理系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"3e5e7d8ae3","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林错误，波匈事件，我国三大害，都是偶然的吗？不，都是一个根源：不民主。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"b775984b46","type":"paragraph","text":"是彻底民主化的时候了，要除三害，便要铲草除根。否则‘野草烧不尽，春风吹又生’是信任人民的时候了，没有人民的绝对权力，没有人民的民主监督，不论如何整风，整来整去，都不过是一阵风；要真正整风，首先要把一切不民主的制度一扫空！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"23d01d9d7b","type":"paragraph","text":"我坚决要求下列民主措施：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"669585af0f","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）严格保证宪法的公民权利。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"ff64da4329","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）人民领导有绝对的实际的监督批评罢免权力。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"8e438c1105","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）反对人事制度的神秘化，专横化，人事工作要受人民监督。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"09632b90ef","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）除政府、军事、及特殊部门外一般不滥行保密，以免借保密而干坏事。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"4abf876bb9","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）反对新闻封锁，压制言论；扩大参考消息发行。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"264600ef33","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）干部政策要德才兼顾，反对党团特权化，反对“盲从便是德”。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"},{"id":"a7e8b02414","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：牛汉、邓九平主编《原上草》（北京：经济日报出版社，1998）。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c"}],"page":{"id":"d543fabb7e","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"6521163f3c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}